', 'Metabolism, Excretion', 'The benefits of using rosuvastatin with protease inhibitors should be carefully weighed against the potentially increased risk of myopathy including rhabdomyolysis.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/162929/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Cabotegravir, Maraviroc, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Rilpivirine, Dolutegravir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, More', 'Ramipril, Valsartan, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Pravastatin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Fenofibrate, Gemfibrozil, More', 1767369485);
